---
// dokumentasi.astro - Public Developer API Documentation
import PenggabungUtama from '../layouts/PenggabungUtama.astro';
---

<PenggabungUtama title="Dokumentasi API | EasyMarket Developer Portal" jsFile="/ecom/js/index.js">
    <div class="docs-hero" id="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="doc-icon-hero"><rect width="20" height="8" x="2" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"/><rect width="20" height="8" x="2" y="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="6" x2="6.01" y1="6" y2="6"/><line x1="6" x2="6.01" y1="18" y2="18"/><line x1="10" x2="10.01" y1="6" y2="6"/><line x1="10" x2="10.01" y1="18" y2="18"/></svg>
                EasyMarket Developer API Portal
            </h1>
            <p>Integrasikan sistem pulsa, paket data, PLN, dan <b>Top-Up Game (Diamonds & Vouchers)</b> langsung ke dalam aplikasi Anda secara instan & White-Label.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="/api_docs.json" download="easymarket_api_docs.json" class="btn btn-download-json">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="btn-icon"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line></svg>
                    Download OpenAPI JSON
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="docs-container">
        <!-- Sidebar Navigation Index -->
        <aside class="docs-toc">
            <div class="toc-card">
                <h3>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="doc-icon"><path d="M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H20v20H6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-2.5-2.5Z"/><path d="M6 6h10M6 10h10"/></svg>
                    Daftar Isi
                </h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#kredensial" class="toc-link">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="doc-icon-toc"><rect width="18" height="11" x="3" y="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
                            Kredensial API
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#kategori-produk" class="toc-link">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="doc-icon-toc"><path d="m7.5 4.27 9 5.15M21 8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16Z"/><path d="m3.3 7 8.7 5 8.7-5M12 22V12"/></svg>
                            Kategori Produk
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li><a href="#endpoint-pricelist" class="toc-link"><span class="badge-method-toc get">GET</span> Get Pricelist</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#endpoint-checkout" class="toc-link"><span class="badge-method-toc post">POST</span> Post Checkout</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#endpoint-status" class="toc-link"><span class="badge-method-toc get">GET</span> Get Order Status</a></li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#contoh-kode" class="toc-link">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="doc-icon-toc"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
                            Contoh Implementasi
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <main class="docs-main">
            <!-- KREDENSIAL -->
            <section id="kredensial" class="doc-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="doc-icon"><rect width="18" height="11" x="3" y="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
                    Kredensial & Autentikasi
                </h2>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>Semua request API memerlukan parameter <code>reseller_key</code> yang disematkan ke dalam request payload untuk autentikasi keamanan. Hubungi Admin EasyMarket untuk mendapatkan key Anda.</p>
                        <div class="api-url-box">
                            <span id="reseller-api-key" style="color: #10b981; font-weight: 700;">DEMO_RESELLER_KEY_X987HSD23</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- KATEGORI PRODUK -->
            <section id="kategori-produk" class="doc-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="doc-icon"><path d="m7.5 4.27 9 5.15M21 8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16Z"/><path d="m3.3 7 8.7 5 8.7-5M12 22V12"/></svg>
                    Kategori Produk yang Tersedia
                </h2>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>Kami menyalurkan transaksi Anda langsung ke vendor terpercaya secara otomatis:</p>
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="doc-table">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Kategori</th>
                                        <th>Deskripsi Layanan</th>
                                        <th>Mendukung Top-Up Game / DM</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><code>pulsa</code></td>
                                        <td>Pulsa reguler untuk seluruh operator (Telkomsel, Indosat, XL, Axis, Tri, Smartfren)</td>
                                        <td>❌ Tidak</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><code>data</code></td>
                                        <td>Paket kuota internet prabayar</td>
                                        <td>❌ Tidak</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><code>pln</code></td>
                                        <td>Token listrik PLN Prabayar</td>
                                        <td>❌ Tidak</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><code>game</code></td>
                                        <td><b>Diamond Game & Voucher</b>: Mobile Legends (ML), Free Fire (FF), PUBG Mobile (PU), Garena Shell (GR)</td>
                                        <td>✅ Ya (Proses Instan)</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- ENDPOINT PRICELIST -->
            <section id="endpoint-pricelist" class="doc-section">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <span class="badge-method badge-get">GET</span>
                        <span>1. Endpoint Daftar Produk (Pricelist)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>Mengambil daftar seluruh produk beserta kode varian, harga modal, kategori, dan status keaktifan.</p>
                        <div class="api-url-box">
                            <span>GET https://api.ilhampradani.me/api/products</span>
                        </div>

                        <h4 class="sub-title">Query Parameters</h4>
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="doc-table">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Parameter</th>
                                        <th>Tipe</th>
                                        <th>Wajib</th>
                                        <th>Keterangan</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><code>category_slug</code></td>
                                        <td>String</td>
                                        <td>Tidak</td>
                                        <td>Filter berdasarkan kategori (e.g. <code>pulsa</code>, <code>data</code>, <code>pln</code>, <code>game</code>)</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>

                        <h4 class="sub-title">Response Sukses (JSON)</h4>
                        <pre><code>{`{
  "success": true,
  "products": [
    {
      "product_code": "TELKOMSEL_PROMO",
      "variant_code": "t5000",
      "name": "Telkomsel Rp 5.000",
      "price": 5750,
      "category": "pulsa",
      "status": "normal"
    },
    {
      "product_code": "MOBILE_LEGENDS",
      "variant_code": "ml_86",
      "name": "Mobile Legends 86 Diamonds",
      "price": 19600,
      "category": "game",
      "status": "normal"
    }
  ]
}`}</code></pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- ENDPOINT CHECKOUT -->
            <section id="endpoint-checkout" class="doc-section">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <span class="badge-method badge-post">POST</span>
                        <span>2. Endpoint Buat Transaksi (Checkout)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>Menginisiasi transaksi baru. Endpoint ini akan mengembalikan link atau data gambar QRIS untuk discan oleh pembeli.</p>
                        <div class="api-url-box">
                            <span>POST https://api.ilhampradani.me/api/checkout</span>
                        </div>

                        <h4 class="sub-title">Request Body (JSON)</h4>
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="doc-table">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Field</th>
                                        <th>Tipe</th>
                                        <th>Wajib</th>
                                        <th>Keterangan</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><code>reseller_key</code></td>
                                        <td>String</td>
                                        <td>Ya</td>
                                        <td>API Key Anda</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><code>whatsapp_id</code></td>
                                        <td>String</td>
                                        <td>Ya</td>
                                        <td>Nomor WA pembeli untuk notifikasi (e.g. <code>081234567890</code>)</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><code>product_code</code></td>
                                        <td>String</td>
                                        <td>Ya</td>
                                        <td>Kode kategori produk (e.g. <code>MOBILE_LEGENDS</code> / <code>TELKOMSEL_PROMO</code>)</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><code>variant_code</code></td>
                                        <td>String</td>
                                        <td>Ya</td>
                                        <td>Kode varian produk (e.g. <code>ml_86</code> / <code>t5000</code>)</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><code>target</code></td>
                                        <td>String</td>
                                        <td>Ya</td>
                                        <td>Nomor HP Tujuan / ID Game Pelanggan. Untuk Game ML: <code>IDUser(ZoneID)</code>, contoh <code>12345678(1234)</code></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><code>amount</code></td>
                                        <td>Number</td>
                                        <td>Ya</td>
                                        <td>Nominal harga yang sesuai dengan pricelist</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>

                        <h4 class="sub-title">Response Sukses (JSON)</h4>
                        <pre><code>{`{
  "success": true,
  "transaction_id": "TRX-PP-992138",
  "qr_image_url": "https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=300&data=...",
  "amount": 19800,
  "provider": "portalpulsa"
}`}</code></pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- ENDPOINT STATUS -->
            <section id="endpoint-status" class="doc-section">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <span class="badge-method badge-get">GET</span>
                        <span>3. Endpoint Cek Status Transaksi</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>Mengambil status pembayaran QRIS dan status fulfillment dari transaksi Anda secara real-time.</p>
                        <div class="api-url-box">
                            <span>GET https://api.ilhampradani.me/api/order/status/&#123;transaction_id&#125;</span>
                        </div>

                        <h4 class="sub-title">Response Status (JSON)</h4>
                        <pre><code>{`{
  "success": true,
  "status": "paid",
  "message": "Fulfillment sukses dikirim ke nomor tujuan",
  "sn": "SN-99823102381203",
  "amount": 19800
}`}</code></pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- CONTOH KODE -->
            <section id="contoh-kode" class="doc-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="doc-icon"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
                    Contoh Implementasi Kode
                </h2>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="sub-title">Menggunakan cURL</h4>
                        <pre><code>{`curl -X POST https://api.ilhampradani.me/api/checkout \\
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \\
  -d '{
    "reseller_key": "DEMO_RESELLER_KEY_X987HSD23",
    "whatsapp_id": "081234567890",
    "product_code": "TELKOMSEL_PROMO",
    "variant_code": "t5000",
    "target": "081299002233",
    "amount": 5750
  }'`}</code></pre>

                        <h4 class="sub-title" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">Menggunakan Python</h4>
                        <pre><code>{`import requests

url = "https://api.ilhampradani.me/api/checkout"
payload = {
    "reseller_key": "DEMO_RESELLER_KEY_X987HSD23",
    "whatsapp_id": "081234567890",
    "product_code": "TELKOMSEL_PROMO",
    "variant_code": "t5000",
    "target": "081299002233",
    "amount": 5750
}
response = requests.post(url, json=payload)
print(response.json())`}</code></pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
</PenggabungUtama>

<style>
    .doc-icon {
        display: inline-block;
        vertical-align: middle;
        margin-right: 8px;
        color: #4f46e5;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .doc-icon-hero {
        display: inline-block;
        vertical-align: middle;
        margin-right: 10px;
        color: #818cf8;
    }

    .doc-icon-toc {
        display: inline-block;
        vertical-align: middle;
        margin-right: 8px;
        color: #64748b;
        transition: color 0.1s;
    }
    .toc-link:hover .doc-icon-toc {
        color: #4f46e5;
    }

    .badge-method-toc {
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        padding: 2px 5px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin-right: 8px;
        display: inline-block;
        vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .badge-method-toc.get {
        background-color: #dcfce7;
        color: #15803d;
    }
    .badge-method-toc.post {
        background-color: #e0e7ff;
        color: #4f46e5;
    }

    .toc-link {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .docs-hero {
        background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('/gambar/luxury_hero.webp');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 8rem 2rem 5rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 2.25rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-content p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #cbd5e1;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .btn-download-json {
        background: #4f46e5;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        border: none;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4);
    }

    .btn-download-json:hover {
        background: #4338ca;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .docs-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 3rem auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
        gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .toc-card {
        background: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        position: sticky;
        top: 2rem;
    }

    .toc-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1e293b;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .toc-card ul {
        list-style: none;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 8px;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .toc-card a {
        color: #475569;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.925rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: color 0.1s;
    }

    .toc-card a:hover {
        color: #4f46e5;
    }

    .docs-main {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .doc-section {
        scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #1e293b;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .card {
        background: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card-header {
        background: #f8fafc;
        padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #1e293b;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
    }

    .card-body {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .sub-title {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #334155;
        border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5;
        padding-left: 8px;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .badge-method {
        padding: 4px 8px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .badge-post {
        background-color: #e0e7ff;
        color: #4f46e5;
    }
    .badge-get {
        background-color: #dcfce7;
        color: #15803d;
    }

    .api-url-box {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 14px;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #334155;
        overflow-x: auto;
        white-space: nowrap;
        -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    }

    pre {
        background: #1e1e24;
        color: #f8fafc;
        padding: 16px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        overflow-x: auto;
        border: 1px solid #2d2d30;
    }

    .table-responsive {
        width: 100%;
        overflow-x: auto;
        -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .doc-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        min-width: 500px;
    }

    .doc-table th, .doc-table td {
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .doc-table th {
        background-color: #f8fafc;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #475569;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .docs-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .docs-toc {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .toc-card {
            position: static;
            padding: 1rem;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-left: none;
            border-right: none;
            border-radius: 0;
            box-shadow: none;
            border-top: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .toc-card h3 {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            padding: 0 0.5rem;
        }
        .toc-card ul {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            overflow-x: auto;
            white-space: nowrap;
            padding: 0 0.5rem 0.5rem 0.5rem;
            margin: 0;
            gap: 8px;
            scrollbar-width: none;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .toc-card ul::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
        .toc-card li {
            display: inline-block;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .toc-card a {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .toc-card a:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .toc-card a:hover .doc-icon-toc {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .docs-main {
            display: flex;
